"ding!"

That's the sound of PostgreSQL NOTIFY telling Go it's time to...

* SMTP-send an email
* HTTP POST a tweet to Bluesky, X, Telegram, and ActivityPub followers
* write new XML (RSS/Atom) to the filesystem
* write new HTML to the filesystem


"ding!"

That's the sound of an incoming HTTP request to my...

* ActivityPub inbox
* WhatsApp endpoint
* Weixin endpoint


Daemons make the "ding!".  It's one "ding" binary that has...

* PostgreSQL listener with many responders
* HTTP server listening to many webhook endpoints
* Telegram TDLib client

... and certainly more to come, like importing incoming emails.


More Go than SQL here because it's more "ding!" network than data.


